{"id": "1410139440181022750", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "Question, do we know what \"Rotation Gap\" is? \nIt appears to be a large chunk of Stage names/descriptions that appear below the Lightless Realm stages in the sheets, and share their naming conventions (Aequor Legacy: Fissure / Aequor Legacy: Rotation Gap)\nEach Realm has 4 stages, all with the same descriptions, then that 4 stages x 4 realms block gets repeated 2 more times.\nIs this unimplemented content?", "timestamp": "2025-08-27T05:50:41.663000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-08-27T05:50:56.124000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1410139440004857917", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 30844, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1410139440004857917/image.png?ex=6a3235b1&is=6a30e431&hm=c1641e7bd63af72156d1b9a9f37f3182cfe7cc055d0bccec1551ca1171345ac7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
