{"id": "1410144211751276585", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "Also, I believe I found another example of the source sheets they gave us being from a previous game version.\nThe Phantasmal Dive stage rows contain descriptions for one category of stage that don't match with the current game. I can't check the others yet because it's not their day right now but I figured I'd note this in case it's relevant to anyone.\nSheet version:\n> `Here lies a university, riddled with scars and weary\\nIt once dedicated hope and courage to humanity's survival\\nAs for the outcome, you can see it now`\nGame version:\n```\"A university lies buried here, riddled with wounds and utterly exhausted. \nIt once dedicated a glimmer of hope and courage to humanity's survival.\nAs for the result, you can see it for yourself now.\"```", "timestamp": "2025-08-27T06:09:39.294000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1410144211520720916", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 422497, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1402941858606219294/1410144211520720916/image.png?ex=6a323a23&is=6a30e8a3&hm=11d3ea9762d56c6daecdc4fddfd4d25d172ed77b2a97945e0e47b8f988b7ceb7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1410145151103402085", "channel_id": "1402941858606219294", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "the other example I had found when I was on call with Jynn the other day, and that was that they appear to have (literally *this* update) fixed one of the first things I was excited to fix myself when I had the opportunity, and that was literally just mass Find-&-Replacing \"Defence\" with \"Defense\"\nevery single instance of Defence in the game right now is completely gone and replaced with Defense\nAND I DIDN'T EVEN NOTICE till I went to fix the Wheels of Destiny and realized the in-game text says Defense and the sheets say Defence but nothing else was different lol.", "timestamp": "2025-08-27T06:13:23.253000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
